Now parents can set daily time limits to help set restrictions on screen time. You can also decide how much time your child can spend watching video so they can spend more time reading. With Learn First parents can block access to entertainment content until after educational goals are met. With the Bedtime feature enabled parents can control when FreeTime shuts down for the day.
